title: Baroque Trumpet Concertos - Sheet Music & Audio
description:
This is a collection of both the SHEET MUSIC and the MP3 AUDIO files of three concertos for baroque trumpet. 

Torelli - Trumpet Concerto in D

Telemann - Trumpet Concerto in D

Fasch - Trumpet Concerto in D

The sheet music for each piece is in PDF format and includes the piano score and parts. It is recommended that these pieces be performed on trumpet in D or piccolo trumpet pitched in A. 

The audio files are high quality 256kps encoded with Lame MP3Pro. The performance is by the legendary and incomparable Maurice Andre.  

These concerti are important works for the instrument and standard repertoire for any student or professional.
